{
  "texts": [
    "Let K be an integer in [2, n], and p, q ∈ (0, 1), with p > q.",
    "We assume that Y * is sampled according to the following distribution:",
    "∼ Uniform {1,.",
    "Conditionally on z 1,.",
    ", z n, the entries (Y * ij) i<j are sampled independently, with Y * ij distributed as a Bernoulli random variable with parameter q + λ1 {z i = z j }, where λ = p -q > 0."
  ]
}